      "text": "made or until a saucer crashes away from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "its home base-which is highly unlikely",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "because of its jet helicopter action that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "makes take-offs and landings almost com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "pletely safe. But there are these facts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "that point to an answer:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Official inquiry by the Air Force, in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "face of overwhelming evidence that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "saucers are real, was called off last De-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "cember. This indicates clearly that Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Force officials know where the saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "originate and are not concerned about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "them, as they would be if these aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "were from Russia or Mars. These officials,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "at the same time, denied emphatically",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "that a secret Air Force project was re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "sponsible.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Best use of fully developed saucer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "aircraft, however, could be made in war-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "time not by the Air Force, but by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Navy. All fleet operations now require",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "an air cover, even in antisubmarine war-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "fare, and a plane that can rise like a heli-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "copter could be used from any combat",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "ship, not only from big, expensive aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "carriers. It was for this reason that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "first U.S. flying saucer was purchased by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the Navy. The original model was tested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "in 1942.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "That first full-size aircraft, built by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Chance-Vought, was thoroughly tested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "by Navy engineers. Then a statement",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "was released that this project had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "dropped. Early experimenting with sau-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "cers, thus, centered in the Navy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Big spending on missile aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "starts in the Navy now, too. More than",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "twice as many dollars were spent by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Navy last year as by the Air Force on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "secret guided-missile research. There is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "no public accounting for these millions,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "the only Government funds aside from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "atomic-energy dollars that still are being",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "spent with great secrecy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Surface indications, then, point to re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "search centers of the U.S. Navy as the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "guided-missile project that is the scene of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "present flying-saucer development. That",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "project has the scientists, the engineers,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "the dollars, the motive, and the back-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "ground of early Navy development of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "saucer-type aircraft. This likelihood will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "remain despite any future denials by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "Navy from now until secrecy is lifted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "on the big missile program.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "But regardless of just where these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "saucers are being built now, the evidence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
