      "text": "points to a U.S. development that will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "mean a radical change in aircraft design",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "in coming decades. In war, this combina-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "tion of helicopter and fast plane will be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "easily outflown by anything now in the",
